Replace the force system by an equivalent resultant force and couple moment at point [`A`]. Express answers in catesian form.
 

[`F_R`] =  ([___]{"$frx"}[`\textbf{i}`]  [`+`] [___]{"$fry"}[`\textbf{j}`]  [`+`] [___]{"$frz"} [`\textbf{k}`])  [`\textrm{N}`]


[`M_A`] =  ([___]{"$Mx"}[`\textbf{i}`]  [`+`] [___]{"$My"}[`\textbf{j}`]  [`+`] [___]{"$Mz"} [`\textbf{k}`]) [`\textrm{N-m}`]

END_PGML

